cords in the kitchen.

00:25:09.840 --> 00:25:12.398
One of my first
professional jobs

00:25:12.398 --> 00:25:15.085
was selling-- I'm
killing my mic,

00:25:15.085 --> 00:25:18.780
I'm sure-- one of my first jobs
was selling cellular phones

